      <akn:section eId="sec_42_1901_04">
        <akn:num>42-1901.04</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Separate taxation.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_42-1901_04_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>If there is any unit owner other than the declarant, a tax or assessment shall not be levied on the condominium as a whole or against any common elements, but only on the individual condominium units. A condominium unit shall be carried on the records of the District of Columbia and assessed as a separate and distinct taxable entity.</akn:p></akn:content>
